      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Horizontal members laid across the bottom of an unfinished opening to act as a base during construction of window frames or door frames. For the horizontal members that rest on the foundation at the bottom of a wood structure, use "sill plates."
</Note_Text>
